org.fax4j.spi.adapter

Class AbstractAdapterFaxClientSpi

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fax4j.spi.AbstractFaxClientSpi
      • org.fax4j.spi.AbstractFax4JClientSpi
        • org.fax4j.spi.adapter.AbstractAdapterFaxClientSpi
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationHolder, FaxClientActions, ProviderImplementation, FaxClientSpi
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdapterFaxClientSpi, WindowsFaxClientSpi

    public abstract class AbstractAdapterFaxClientSpi
extends AbstractFax4JClientSpi
    This class provides partial implementation of an adapter fax client service provider interface.
    This implementation will proxy the requests to another internal SPI.
    Since:
    0.41.5
    Version:
    1.01
    Author:
    Sagie Gur-Ari
